    "Table 11 details the leaderboard evaluation configuration and the experimental settings applied in this study.",
    "AlpacaEval is an automated evaluation benchmark for LLMs, employing GPT-4 (OpenAI, 2023) as an annotator to compare the responses generated by the models against reference answers produced by text-davinci-003.",
